{"type":null,"faqId":45306,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的 4K 视频资源多吗？对电视机和网络是否有特殊要求？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀盒子M321自带 4K 专区，视频资源会持续更新，越来越多。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>荣耀盒子M321上的所有视频（4K 及 非 4K）都能在普通电视机上观看。网速不低于 4M 时能流畅的观看高清视频。但如果您想流畅的观看真 4K 视频，还需要另外满足如下条件：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">电视机要求：</span><span>电视机需要支持 4K（</span><span class=\"s2\">4K 电视机</span><span>），才能享受到真正 4K 视频的震撼清晰度。非 4K 电视看 4K 视频只能达到电视机所能支持的最高清晰度（如：1080P，1080I，720P）。但是并不能达到真正 4K 视频的显示效果。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">网络要求：不低于 10M 网速</span><span>，观看 4K 视频，网络需稳定且不能低于 10M。您可以进入“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 网络 &gt; 网络测速</span><span>”来检测您的网速是否符合要求，测速结果会告诉您当前的网络环境适合播放哪种清晰度的视频。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164829\" style=\"width:4.3729167in;height:2.4631944in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":243,"faqType":"本地播放","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"827","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Local-Storage-Play","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556872000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":57,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"4K,视频资源,网络要求,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}